      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and double VANOS, delivering a crisp throttle response and a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, with recent cooling system service and an inspection of the rear subframe mounting points. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are optimized for immediate performance and driver engagement.",
